tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE demographic_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    city VARCHAR(50),
    occupation VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE person (
    person_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(50),
    last_name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    occupation VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE address (
    address_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    person_id INT REFERENCES person(person_id),
    street VARCHAR(100),
    city VARCHAR(50),
    state VARCHAR(50),
    postal_code VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE demographic_data (
    person_id INT REFERENCES person(person_id),
    income DECIMAL(10, 2),
    education_level VARCHAR(50),
    marital_status VARCHAR(20),
    ethnicity VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE policy_decision (
    decision_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    decision_description TEXT,
    approval_date DATE,
    person_id INT REFERENCES person(person_id)
)

CREATE TABLE demographics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR,
    income DECIMAL,
    location VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE education (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    level VARCHAR,
    field_of_study VARCHAR,
    graduation_year INT,
    institution VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE employment (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    company_name VARCHAR,
    position VARCHAR,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE family (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    family_size INT,
    spouse_gender VARCHAR,
    children_count INT,
    income_level DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE residence (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    address VARCHAR,
    zipcode VARCHAR,
    city VARCHAR,
    state VARCHAR
);
